Install Tomcat:
https://linuxize.com/post/how-to-install-tomcat-9-on-ubuntu-18-04/#step-4-create-a-systemd-unit-file

Install Eclipse:
sudo apt install snapd
sudo snap install eclipse --classic

In Eclipse:
Help->Install New Software
Work with: https://projects.eclipse.org/releases/2019-03
In "Web, XML, Java EE and OSGi Enterprise Development" install:
Eclipse Java EE Developer Tools
Eclipse Java Web Developer Tools
Eclipse Web Developer Tools
Eclipse XML Editors and Tools
JST Server Adapters
JST Server Adapters 

